{"tid":2223963,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"☆我係中共一定好開心，十月一有咁多人同我慶祝生日☆","createTime":"2020-09-30T07:51:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T08:06:08.000Z","uid":211994,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"630a5ebcdc85256629647edcb1a1fd4d1b5e2e4b","tid":2223963,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T07:51:21.000Z","msg":"全球63個城市，23個國家揀正我生日遊行<br />\n今舖真係開心到瞓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CFt8wzLHBD1/?igshid=1m655vhzfky2i\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCFt8wzLHBD1%2F%3Figshid%3D1m655vhzfky2i&d=uIqzu4H250jM%2FFVIgxmQWOQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=3de83a17\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCFt8wzLHBD1%2F%3Figshid%3D1m655vhzfky2i&h=c043599b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CFt8wzLHBD1/?igshid=1m655vhzfky2i</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NZakDJh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNZakDJh.png&h=8e35ebb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PdvdegE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPdvdegE.png&h=84a9e9ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">香港當日都有活動，請大家留意活動風險極高，手足應確保自己有完整計劃，心理生理亦應準備好<br />\n只要有一絲猶豫同未準備好（未練好身體/裝備唔夠/覺得今次唔應該出）都應慎重審視自己要唔要上街<br />\n和理非亦應該落街幫手睇下有冇野狗，唔好由得勇武手足喺街上活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/urom7DL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Furom7DL.jpg&h=573f9491&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MRggb5q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMRggb5q.jpg&h=3e4077aa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Zim7DM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Zim7DM.jpg&h=24ae1530&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c12a7ac2e2d806143c1ebb77ce83347997c4d07b","tid":2223963,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T07:51:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c04099152b79619329e8ec618b3b6d57c2fb5ae","tid":2223963,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T07:52:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"575a1a58895cca44a373c820fbf5f4ee5072b838","tid":2223963,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T07:52:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a68d90e2db8bc8bd9dbb68417515c0af6f0a4316","tid":2223963,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T07:53:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9931d2d15c16256498669009419af69ecc2cdf27","tid":2223963,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T07:53:42.000Z","msg":"全城賀中秋🥮"},{"pid":"a7f6e4c9f7f2a3884e941ebccf954f15356e80b7","tid":2223963,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T07:54:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"549f2108e2bcf6eac516f9ebabfc7b35f2032908","tid":2223963,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T07:54:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9bff3a027dc81fce81e49cf8508153b3b8e87b8","tid":2223963,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T07:54:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"75f91fe3b6a53889475621357585a8930861386b","tid":2223963,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T07:57:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"324c864c3e7933d2d44921bbd20c49d3737ef2e3","tid":2223963,"uid":353256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T08:00:11.000Z","msg":"10月1唔係支共生日，係支共奪權紀念日"},{"pid":"f4b69742ef06ba0d90690d09a17e4c0f1540dfb5","tid":2223963,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T08:03:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src